data.description: This charming and luminous Weston Doll House is situated within the desirable Savanna Subdivision, boasting a wealth of amenities. The property features a brand-new roof installed in June 2021, along with complete accordion shutters for added security and convenience. Nestled in a peaceful and serene environment, the house is complemented by beautiful landscaping, elegant crown moldings, modern stainless-steel appliances, an air conditioned 2 car garage, and a nice screened in porch in the rear of the property.
